:h3.Manual Selection
.sp
:i1.browse
:i1.edit 
:p.When options 1 and 2 are selected a list of all available manuals
is supplied.  The user is allowed to select a manual for processing
by placing a 'S' in front of the desired Manual ID.  The Manual
Selection panel is scrollable with the use of PF Keys or commands.
