|    Manual Title (1) |  Y  | Title of the manual.  All three title fields are    |
|    Manual Title (2) |  N  | are used to build the scan file.  Any value sep-    |
|    Manual Title (3) |  N  | by spaces will be used as a keyword.                |
|    Keywords         |  N  | Allows additional keywords that are not in the      |
|                     |     | manual title to be added to the keyword scan file.  |
|                     |     | Allows program numbers to be identified for manuals.|
|    Program No(s)    |     | A maximum of four per manual may be entered. These  |
|                     |     | are informational and not used for any reporting or |
|                     |     | keyword scanning.                                   |
|---------------------+-----+-----------------------------------------------------|
