:h2.KEYWORD (OPTION 3.2)
.sp 3
:i1.keywords
:i1.scan 
:i1.owner
:p.The owner of the library and the SLSS administrator are the only
users allowed to select this option.
This option will rebuild the keyword scan file to be used by primary
Option 'S' (SCAN).  The user is warned when invoking this option
that it could require several minutes to complete.  The reason for
this is that the Manual Title(s) and Keywords fields are
parsed and each word is placed
in the keyword file along with the Manual ID.  The value of
a space is used as the delimiter when the fields are parsed.
.sp
:p.Once the option is selected the following panel is displayed.
.*
.*
.bf GT15 
:fig id=opt032  frame=none place=inline
 
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|                                                                                 |
| ------------ SLSS (Warning Message) ------------------------------------------- |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                 *---------------------------------------------*                 |
|                 |               W A R N I N G                 |                 |
|                 |---------------------------------------------|                 |
|                 |   Please read the following:                |                 |
|                 *---------------------------------------------*                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                 SELECTED OPTION WILL REQUIRE SEVERAL MINUTES                    |
|                 TO COMPLETE.  PLEASE INSURE THAT YOU WANT TO                    |
|                 RUN SELECTED OPTION.                                            |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
|                                                                                 |
| PRESS ENTER TO CONTINUE, END KEY TO TERMINATE                                   |
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
:figcap.Keyword Build Panel
:efig
.pf
.sp
:p.The user must confirm the build keyword request or cancel.
Confirm the request by pressing the enter key.
Cancel the request pressing the END PF Key or entering the end
command. 
.sp
:i1.print
:i1.utility
:p.As the keyword file is being build the user is informed with a
message after every ten manuals have been processed that the
utility is still processing.  This is to let the user known that
their TSO session is still operating.
.*
:h2.PRINT (OPTION 3.3)
.sp 3
:p.This option will produce two different reports, sequential listing
or an on order report.  The user is prompted to supply the
request for which report and supply all other fields on the
panel.
.sp
:i1.print
:i1.sort 
:p.Once the option is selected the following panel is displayed.
.*
.*
