.pf
:h1.CLIST Hierarchy
.fo on
.sp 3
:p.The following supplies the CLIST hierarchy along with the
panels and tables used in each CLIST.
.sp
:p.Several panels are used through out the SLSS system to
supply error, warning, caution and processing messages.  These
panels are SLSS@ERR, SLSS@WRN, SLSS@CAU and SLSS@PRC.  These
panels are not listed below in the hierarchy chart.
.sp
:p.If a CLIST invokes another CLIST, the called CLIST is in
small letters and indented below the invoking CLIST.
.sp
:p.Table name &SLSS is used to signify that the library name
from panel SLSSPRIM is used as the table name.  The &SLSS
value may also be followed by ENQ, SCAN or LOCS.
.sp 2
.fo off
.bf GT12 
  -------------------------------------------------------------------
 |  CLIST         PANEL         TABLE          'TB' Function         |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSINIT       SLSS1TIM      SLSSCNTL    CREATE,ADD,CLOSE          |
 |               SLSS2TIM      SLSSADMN    CREATE,ADD,CLOSE          |
 |                                                                   |
 |The above CLIST is invoked once to initialize the SLSS system and  |
 |is not used again.                                                 |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSS           SLSS@TOP      SLSSADMN    OPEN,SKIP,END,ADD         |
 |  slssopt1     SLSSPRIM      SLSSSL@$    CREATE,ADD,END,VCLEAR,TOP,|
 |  slssopt2     SLSSNEWT         "        SARG,SCAN,MOD,SKIP        |
 |  slssdelt     SLSSMSTR      SLSSCNTL    OPEN,SKIP,END,MOD,VCLEAR, |
 |  slsskeyw     SLSSUTIL         "        BOTTOM,GET,CLOSE          |
 |  slssprnt     SLSSBRWS                                            |
 |  slsssort     SLSSUPDT                                            |
 |  slssrcov     SLSSMODL                                            |
 |  slssopts                                                         |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSOPT1       SLSSBROW      &SLSS       DISPL,TOP,VCLEAR,SARG,    |
 |               SLSSBRW2        "         SCAN                      |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSOPT2       SLSS          &SLSS       OPEN,END,CREATE,QUERY,    |
 |  slsschkv     SLSSADD         "         SORT,MOD,DISPL,GET,SAVE,  |
 |  slsskeyu     SLSSLOCS        "         VCLEAR,ADD,DELETE         |
 |                             &SLSS.ENQ   OPEN,CREATE,SKIP,PUT,SAVE,|
 |                               "         END,ADD,CLOSE             |
 |                             &SLSS.SCAN  CLOSE,CREATE              |
 |                             &SLSS.LOCS  OPEN,CREATE,END,MOD,CLOSE |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSCHKV       SLSSSORT      &SLSS.SAVE  CREATE,END,VCLEAR,ADD,    |
 |                               "         SKIP,SAVE,ERASE           |
 |                             &SLSS       TOP,SKIP,ERASE,VCLEAR,ADD,|
 |                               "         CREATE,SORT,SAVE          |
 |                             &SLSS.SCAN  CLOSE,CREATE              |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSKEYU                     &SLSS.SCAN  OPEN,CLOSE,SORT,SARG,SCAN,|
 |                               "         ADD,MOD,TOP,VCLEAR,DELETE |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSDELT       SLSSDELT      SLSSSL@$    QUERY,DELETE              |
 |               SLSSDELS      SLSSCNTL    OPEN,END,DELETE,GET       |
 |                             &SLSS       ERASE                     |
 |                             &SLSS.SCAN  ERASE                     |
 |                             &SLSS.LOCS  ERASE                     |
 |                             &SLSS.ENQ   ERASE                     |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSKEYW       SLSS@KEY      &SLSS.SCAN  END,ERASE,CREATE,TOP,ADD, |
 |                               "         MOD,CLOSE,SORT,SAVE,SARG, |
 |                                         SCAN,VCLEAR               |
 |                             &SLSS       OPEN,END,SKIP,GET         |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSPRNT       SLSSPRNT      &SLSS       OPEN,SKIP,END             |
 |  slssonor                                                         |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSONOR                     &SLSS       OPEN,SKIP,END             |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSSORT       SLSSSORT      &SLSS       OPEN,DELETE,ADD,SORT,SKIP,|
 |                               "         TOP,GET,BOTTOM,CLOSE      |
 |                                                                   |
 |-------------------------------------------------------------------|
 |                                                                   |
 |SLSSRCOV       SLSSRCOV      &SLSS       END                       |
 |                             &SLSS.ENQ   OPEN,END,SKIP,PUT,CLOSE   |
 |                             &SLSS.SCAN  END                       |
 |                             &SLSS.LOCS  END                       |
 |                                                                   |
